- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions an algorithm implemented in a tool (Parasim) and demonstrates its application on case studies. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper deals with temporal logic and freezing of values, which are relevant to control systems. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper introduces a new logic and discusses its implementation in a tool. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with temporal logic and its application in case studies, which could be related to AI.
